WSC2-Compact-LS (codecs/dragino/wsc2-compact-ls)
------------------------------------------------
This device is not present in TheThingsNetwork/lorawan-devices. Its normalized
codec was authored from Dragino's published payload decoder and product manual:
  https://github.com/dragino/dragino-end-node-decoder (WSC2-Compact-LS)
  https://wiki.dragino.com (WSC2-Compact-LS Weather Station Kit User Manual)
A verbatim copy of the Dragino decoder is retained as an authoring reference at
codecs/dragino/wsc2-compact-ls/reference/upstream-codec.js (excluded from the
published package). Wire-format facts are not copyrightable; the normalized
codec is original work under AGPL-3.0-or-later.

RBS306-VSHB (codecs/radio-bridge/rbs306-vshb)
---------------------------------------------
The MultiTech / Radio Bridge RBS306-VSHB high-bandwidth vibration sensor is not
decoded by the shared radio_bridge_packet_decoder.js used by the other
RadioBridge devices. Its wire format was understood from the official
MIT-licensed decoder:
  @radiobridge/packet-decoder — https://github.com/RadioBridge/Packet-Decoder
  (src/decoders/HBVibrationSensor.ts; MIT License, Copyright (c) Radio Bridge Inc.)
A faithful reference port is retained at
codecs/radio-bridge/rbs306-vshb/reference/upstream-codec.js (excluded from the
published package). MIT is compatible inbound to AGPL-3.0-or-later. Wire-format
facts are not copyrightable; the normalized codec is original work.
